26
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:34,280
Nakakahiya talaga pero ayokong magkamali siya.

27
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:38,250
- Hindi, sa tingin ko hindi ito magiging posible.
- Bakit hindi?

28
00:02:38,250 --> 00:02:41,690
Paumanhin ngunit ang aming priority number one ay palaging

29
00:02:41,690 --> 00:02:43,340
3. Ina, 2. Yumi, 1. Gu Wung

30
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:45,220
Wung.

31
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:52,940
♫ Takot akong masaktan ka kaya sumiksik ako sa gap​ ♫

32
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:55,680
♫ Pinutol ang aking pagkabigo ♫

33
00:02:55,680 --> 00:03:00,150
- Yumi—
- Wala tayong masasabi na makakasakit sa pride ni Wung.

34
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:03,600
♫ Actually wala na akong alam​ ♫

35
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:09,550
♫ Sana ngumiti ka para sa akin ♫

36
